		<title lang="en"><![CDATA[bbDKP 1.1.1]]></title>
		<description lang="en"><![CDATA[bbDKP is a PHPBB3-based DKP solution, evolved from EQDKP to help guilds in MMORPGs (Massive(ly) Multiplayer Online Role-playing Games) track guild members attendance, item purchases and other statistics. It updates and brings together the Dkp/game managment facilites of EQdkp, and integrates them with phpBB3's facilites. This means your users gain single sign on to dkp and phpbb, and you as an administrator or raidleader gain a clean interface, robust admin facilities and less integration headaches. Games supported : Aion, Daoc, Eq, Eq2, ffxi, lotro, vanguard, warhammer, Wow. Features : Multiple Dkp Pools and guilds, DKP Standings, Raids, Events, Item values, Item history, Raid Stats, Bossprogress, Roster, backup, import from eqdkp+. Plugins : Armory Import (Wow & Aion), bbTips (Wow), Raidtracker (wow), Apply.  
This release was completely rewritten, for details see the changelog. 

Further development requests, support questions are welcome at http://www.bbdkp.com. 
As of the current release, it does not (yet) make coffee ;)

