		<author-notes lang="en"><![CDATA[Requirements : phpBB3 v3.0.x, PHP 5 with Libxml 2.6.0 (simplexml usage), Curl 

Please Backup your phpbb3 installation and database before beginning. 
1) If you had 1.0.9rc1 or 1.1-RC before, uninstall it (not the db!). If you're using automod for uninstalling, first restore any folders you might have removed/renamed such as Install.   
2) Then remove the old files to not clutter up your install. 
3) Then install 1.1 with Automod to copy the files and do the core edits. There are considerably less core edits than before. 
4) See DYI section]]></author-notes>
